&= \left( \frac{3F}{8 \sqrt{2m}} \right)^{2/3} \cdot \frac{2}{3} \left( \frac{8 \sqrt{2m}}{3F} E^{3/2} \right)^{-1/3} = \frac{F}{4 \sqrt{2mE}} \\
