由泊松定理可得

$$
\begin{aligned}
F_8 &= \left[F_2, F_5\right] = \left[x p_y - y p_x, \frac{1}{2m} p_x^2 + \frac{1}{2} k x^2\right] \\
&= \frac{1}{m} p_y p_x - \frac{1}{2} k y (-2x) = \frac{1}{m} p_x p_y + k xy = C_8
\end{aligned}
$$

由对称性可得

$$
\begin{aligned}
F_9 &= \frac{1}{m} p_y p_z + k yz = C_9 \\
F_{10} &= \frac{1}{m} p_x p_z + k xz = C_{10}
\end{aligned}
$$

最后，通过泊松定理确认不能再用这些运动积分得到新的运动积分。
